福尔摩斯知道在哪里找我
Holmes knows where to find me

187
00:12:39,898 --> 00:12:41,348
在剧院 别来这里
at the theatre not here,

188
00:12:41,385 --> 00:12:43,248
别再来这里了 医生 你听明白了么?
never here Doctor, do you understand?

189
00:12:43,285 --> 00:12:46,109
在这行当 你树了不少敌人吧
You have enemies in your line of work.

190
00:12:46,683 --> 00:12:49,714
每个人都有敌人 不管他们是干什么的
Everyone has enemies whatever they do,

191
00:12:49,751 --> 00:12:51,625
真实的生活就是这样
is that not true of life.

192
00:12:52,424 --> 00:12:54,156
但有些人冒的风险更高
But some are more at risk than others

193
00:12:54,232 --> 00:12:56,034
由于他们的信念
with their beliefs

194
00:12:56,111 --> 00:12:58,815
和他们的勇气
and their courage.

195
00:12:58,894 --> 00:13:01,598
我做我该做的 医生
I do what I do, Doctor,

196
00:13:01,678 --> 00:13:04,773
别要求我做一个圣徒
don't make me out to be a saint.

197
00:13:04,844 --> 00:13:06,896
现在请容我失陪了
Now please excuse me.

198
00:13:26,867 --> 00:13:30,819
Signor Zamba 是纽约的主要水果出口公司
Signor Zamba, senior partner in the firm of Castallote and Zamba,

199
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,300
Castallote & Zamba公司的高级合伙人
chief fruit importers of New York

200
00:13:33,373 --> 00:13:36,076
最近在他家公寓前的台阶上被刺杀
was stabbed repeatedly on the steps of his mansion.

201
00:13:36,156 --> 00:13:39,346
这事发生在8周之前
Now this is dated eight weeks ago.

202
00:13:39,427 --> 00:13:41,640
平克顿侦探事务所的侦探Rimmer
Detective Rimmer of the Pinkerton Agency,

203
00:13:41,677 --> 00:13:42,415
Abe Rimmer
Abe Rimmer.

204
00:13:42,452 --> 00:13:43,652
在犯罪现场表示
Said at the scene of the slaying

205
00:13:43,688 --> 00:13:46,561
这件事是那不勒斯的帮会所为
we believe this is the work of a Neapolitan society

206
00:13:46,599 --> 00:13:50,728
其与烧炭党联合后 以红圈会闻名于世
allied to the old Carbonari known as the Red Circle.

207
00:13:50,804 --> 00:13:52,050
全欧洲都知道
Famous throughout Europe

208
00:13:52,087 --> 00:13:54,799
现在在布鲁克林也发展了一个分支
a branch is now being planted in Brooklyn.

209
00:13:54,873 --> 00:13:59,089
侦探们地怀疑一个叫Giuseppe Gorgiano的人
Detectives are anxious to question a Giuseppe Gorgiano.

210
00:13:59,126 --> 00:14:00,889
Firmani可能还隐瞒了什么事
Now, Firmani was hiding something else.

211
00:14:00,926 --> 00:14:01,856
我说不出来这种感觉
I can't describe the feeling

212
00:14:01,893 --> 00:14:04,674
但那还有一个老妇人 我推测是他的母亲
but there was an old woman who I took to be his mother.

213
00:14:04,755 --> 00:14:06,213
他的母亲?
His mother?

214
00:14:06,286 --> 00:14:07,389
你去他的家里了?
You went to his home?

215
00:14:07,468 --> 00:14:09,484
是的
Yes.

216
00:14:09,556 --> 00:14:12,225
那张写满悲伤和秘密的脸
A face full of sorrow and secrets.

217
00:14:12,305 --> 00:14:14,285
你帮助的就是这个人么 福尔摩斯?
Is this the person that you helped, Holmes?

218
00:14:14,357 --> 00:14:15,363
如果你对我隐瞒了什么
If you're holding something back

219
00:14:15,399 --> 00:14:17,082
我希望你能告诉我
I should like you to tell me.

220
00:14:20,306 --> 00:14:22,210
你去他的家里
By going to his home

221
00:14:24,029 --> 00:14:26,698
可能会给Firmani带来死亡的威胁
you may have put Firmani's life in danger.

222
00:14:26,778 --> 00:14:28,307
什么?
What?

223
00:14:30,152 --> 00:14:34,080
他为那些在伦敦的意大利人提供庇护
He's a point of refuge for the Italian community in London,

224
00:14:34,535 --> 00:14:36,587
像是灯塔发出来的光
a beacon of light if you will

225
00:14:36,658 --> 00:14:38,825
在这张罪恶的黑网中
in a dark web of devilry.

226
00:14:39,998 --> 00:14:41,658
红圈会
The Red Circle.

227
00:14:44,208 --> 00:14:45,346
天呐
God.

228
00:14:46,609 --> 00:14:48,103
是这个Gorgiano么?
And this Gorgiano?

229
00:14:48,174 --> 00:14:51,649
Black Gorgiano
Black Gorgiano,

230
00:14:51,723 --> 00:14:54,154
有死神之称
he's earned the name of death,

231
00:14:54,227 --> 00:14:59,434
在南意大利和更远地方
La Morte in Southern Italy and far beyond.

232
00:14:59,516 --> 00:15:03,858
是很有名的杀手
He's red up to the elbows in murder.

233
00:15:03,934 --> 00:15:06,365
有没有可能这个Black Gorgiano
Is it possible that this Black Gorgiano

234
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,396
就是Warren太太的房客?
is the man at Mr. Warren's?

235
00:15:07,433 --> 00:15:08,642
不是的 但有着某种联系
No, but there may be some connection.

236
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:10,642
华生 我们有事要做了
Watson, we have work to do.

237
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:12,655
去歌剧院
The opera house.

238
00:15:12,691 --> 00:15:14,103
然后在查令街十字
And then Charing Cross

239
00:15:14,141 --> 00:15:17,478
给我的朋友Abe Rimmer发一封电报
to send a telegram to my friend Abe Rimmer.

240
00:15:41,857 --> 00:15:43,351
非常好 Laven小姐
Wonderful, Miss. Laven,

241
00:15:43,422 --> 00:15:45,260
请再来一遍
just once more, please.

242
00:15:53,859 --> 00:15:56,006
Enrico Firmani
Enrico Firmani.

243
00:16:01,375 --> 00:16:05,290
你一直和我作对
You have been troublesome to me for a long time.

244
00:16:06,212 --> 00:16:08,239
现在你帮我
But now you help me

245
00:16:08,995 --> 00:16:11,858
就饶你一条命
in return for your life,

246
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:15,036
Gennaro Lucca
Gennaro Lucca,

247
00:16:15,535 --> 00:16:17,731
你把他藏到哪去了?
where are you hiding him?

248
00:16:19,083 --> 00:16:20,974
你到底说还是不说 Enrico?
Will you tell me, Enrico?

249
00:16:50,048 --> 00:16:51,648
这里不容许通行
Nobody's allowed in here.

250
00:16:51,961 --> 00:16:54,143
哦 是你 福尔摩斯先生
Oh, it's you, Mr. Holmes.

251
00:16:59,615 --> 00:17:01,406
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes.

252
00:17:01,772 --> 00:17:03,539
Hawkins 你怎么到这来了?
Hawkins, what brings you here?

253
00:17:03,617 --> 00:17:05,764
我想和你来的理由一样
Same thing that brings you I expect.

254
00:17:05,843 --> 00:17:07,990
我无法想象您这么快就接手这个案子
How you got onto it so fast I can't imagine.

255
00:17:08,071 --> 00:17:09,979
不同的线索
Different threads

256
00:17:10,052 --> 00:17:11,996
把我们引到了同一场纷争里
leading up to the same tangle.

257
00:17:12,071 --> 00:17:14,253
我们是来找Enrico Firmani的
We've come to see Enrico Firmani.

258
00:17:14,332 --> 00:17:16,657
他已经死了
But Firmani's dead.

259
00:17:16,733 --> 00:17:20,237
在还不到2小时前 在这里被人割断了喉咙
He was found with his throat cut less than two hours ago up here.

260
00:17:20,978 --> 00:17:23,581
恐怕凶手已经逃得无影无踪了
Murderer got clean away I'm afraid.

261
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:25,770
华生
Watson.

262
00:17:37,956 --> 00:17:39,524
你说中了 福尔摩斯
You're right, Holmes,

263
00:17:40,878 --> 00:17:43,060
我今早不该去找他的
I should not have gone this morning.

264
00:17:43,696 --> 00:17:45,638
或许能救他一命
Might have saved a life.

265
00:17:46,062 --> 00:17:48,581
我想这不该怪罪于你
I don't think you can blame yourself for that.

266
00:17:50,515 --> 00:17:58,267
才子娇娃同归泉壤 正像扫烟囱人一样
Golden boys and girls all must as chimneysweeps come to dust.

267
00:17:50,515 --> 00:17:58,267
<i>(莎士比亚<辛白林> 此处用朱生豪译文)</i>
Golden boys and girls all must as chimneysweeps come to dust.

268
00:18:06,136 --> 00:18:08,959
一个人孤身来到伦敦
A person arrives alone in London.

269
00:18:09,095 --> 00:18:11,110
他去找Firmani寻求帮助
He seeks help from Firmani,

270
00:18:11,181 --> 00:18:12,032
他的同乡为了安全起见
his fellow countryman

271
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:14,896
安排他住在Warren太太的公寓里
who places him for safety in Mrs. Warren's lodgings.

272
00:18:14,974 --> 00:18:18,387
紧接着Firmani被谋杀了
And then Firmani is murdered

273
00:18:18,424 --> 00:18:20,462
是因为不肯说出这个藏身之处
rather than give away the hiding place.

274
00:18:20,540 --> 00:18:22,966
不 不
No, no.

275
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:25,193
还不能肯定这一点
Of that we can't be sure.

276
00:18:26,698 --> 00:18:28,353
那是谁杀了他呢?
But who killed him?

277
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,126
Gorgiano?
Gorgiano?

278
00:18:30,872 --> 00:18:32,747
Gorgiano在英国么?
Is Gorgiano in England?

279
00:18:33,204 --> 00:18:35,142
他想把这个房客怎么样?
What does he want with this lodger?

280
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:38,434
公寓房间里的那个人 完全孤立 很危险
The person in that room is entirely alone and at risk,

281
00:18:38,471 --> 00:18:40,610
甚至写一封信都可能被截获
I mean even a letter might be intercepted.

282
00:18:40,719 --> 00:18:43,699
那么他是怎么收到外面的消息?
How does a message reach him from the outside?

283
00:18:43,736 --> 00:18:47,894
除非是通过那个最有价值的猎场
Except by that most valuable hunting ground

284
00:18:47,931 --> 00:18:51,131
甚至对那些不同寻常的学者来说
ever given to the student of the unusual.

285
00:18:51,168 --> 00:18:52,599
报上的广告栏
Agony columns.

286
00:18:52,636 --> 00:18:56,487
我们只需要把注意力放在
We need only concern ourselves

287
00:18:56,524 --> 00:18:58,922
过去两周的
with the Daily Chronicle.

288
00:18:59,649 --> 00:19:01,858
每日新闻报上
For the past two weeks,

289
00:19:01,895 --> 00:19:05,328
我们的房客每天早饭后
which our lodger collects every morning

290
00:19:05,970 --> 00:19:08,266
都要翻阅它的
after his breakfast.

291
00:19:10,243 --> 00:19:12,303
哦 天呐
Oh, dear me,

292
00:19:13,005 --> 00:19:16,031
好一个喊叫和呻吟的大合唱
what a chorus of cries and groans.

293
00:19:16,067 --> 00:19:20,192
好一堆怪事奇闻的大杂烩
What a ragbag of singular happenings.

294
00:19:23,026 --> 00:19:24,664
在王子滑冰俱乐部...
Lady with a feather boa

295
00:19:25,665 --> 00:19:28,301
戴黑色羽毛围巾的女士
at Prince's Skating Club.

296
00:19:29,313 --> 00:19:30,990
福尔摩斯 听听这个
Holmes, listen to this,

297
00:19:31,759 --> 00:19:34,958
耐心点 将寻找一种可靠的通信方法
Be patient, will find some means of communications,

298
00:19:34,994 --> 00:19:37,484
目前仍用此栏 G
meanwhile this column G.

299
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,153
你能再沿着这条线索找下去吗?
Can you pick up a trace again?

300
00:19:42,230 --> 00:19:43,536
噢 有了
Ah, here we are.

301
00:19:45,466 --> 00:19:48,560
正在做有效安排
I'm making successful arrangements,

302
00:19:48,631 --> 00:19:50,220
请耐心谨慎
patience and prudence,

303
00:19:50,301 --> 00:19:52,697
乌云就会散去 G
the clouds will pass G.

304
00:19:56,147 --> 00:19:57,250
哦 没有了
No, nothing.

305
00:20:01,644 --> 00:20:04,182
在这 道路已清除
Here, here, the path is clearing.

306
00:20:04,253 --> 00:20:06,329
如有机会 当发信号
If I find chance to signal message

307
00:20:06,409 --> 00:20:08,247
记住说定的暗号
remember code as agreed,

308
00:20:08,323 --> 00:20:10,470
这是两天前的
that's two days ago.

309
00:20:12,394 --> 00:20:13,674
Hudson太太?
Mrs. Hudson?

310
00:20:15,177 --> 00:20:16,862
有什么事 福尔摩斯先生?
What is it, Mr. Holmes?

311
00:20:16,898 --> 00:20:18,303
我正洗窗帘呢
I'm washing curtains.

312
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:20,206
请找一下昨天和今天的每日新闻报
The Daily Chronicle yesterday and today,

313
00:20:20,243 --> 00:20:22,116
如果你乐意的话
if you'd be so kind.

314
00:20:23,992 --> 00:20:25,713
耐心谨慎
Patience and prudence.

315
00:20:26,067 --> 00:20:29,641
现在这事终于有点眉目了
Now the affair begins to grow more intelligible.

316
00:21:24,934 --> 00:21:26,737
我找到了
I've found it.

317
00:21:26,812 --> 00:21:29,385
带门廊和黑门的房子 第二层
House with porch and black door, first floor,

318
00:21:29,456 --> 00:21:32,302
窗户右边 黄昏后 G
window right, after dusk, G.

319
00:21:32,379 --> 00:21:33,624
你看
There you are.

320
00:21:33,701 --> 00:21:36,647
G... Black Gorgiano
G, Black Gorgiano.

321
00:21:36,728 --> 00:21:38,840
可能会是个陷阱 来引那个人出去?
Could it be a trap, to draw the person out?

322
00:21:38,877 --> 00:21:39,758
不大可能
Unlikely.

323
00:21:39,939 --> 00:21:42,312
我们是不是该把已经知道的 红圈会的事告诉警察
Well should we not tell the police what we know about the Red Circle?

324
00:21:42,349 --> 00:21:43,838
告诉警察?
Tell the police,

325
00:21:44,044 --> 00:21:46,167
他们手头的事就够他们受的了
they find it difficult enough to deal with the facts

326
00:21:46,204 --> 00:21:49,995
别用我们的想法来让他们更困惑
without confusing them with our suppositions.

327
00:21:50,032 --> 00:21:51,270
听听这个
Oh, listen to this,

328
00:21:51,583 --> 00:21:53,271
毫无动机的谋杀
motiveless murder.

329
00:21:53,462 --> 00:21:56,575
根据对Hawkins警督的采访 真是
According to Inspector Hawkins, really.

330
00:21:57,116 --> 00:21:59,737
福尔摩斯先生 医生 你最好快一点
Mr. Holmes, Doctor, you must come quickly,

331
00:21:59,774 --> 00:22:01,732
有人被绑架了
there's been a kidnapping.

332
00:22:02,856 --> 00:22:04,908
应该交给警察 福尔摩斯先生
This is a police matter, Mr. Holmes.

333
00:22:04,979 --> 00:22:06,780
我要把那个房客赶出去
I'm throwing that lodger out.

334
00:22:06,857 --> 00:22:08,729
我该去和他直说了
I'd have gone straight up and told him so...

335
00:22:08,805 --> 00:22:10,276
但她认为应该
But she thought it only right

336
00:22:10,313 --> 00:22:12,837
先征求您的意见 福尔摩斯先生
to ask your opinion first, Mr. Holmes.

337
00:22:12,911 --> 00:22:15,296
请泡一壶茶 Hudson太太
A large pot of tea please, Mrs. Hudson.

338
00:22:18,443 --> 00:22:22,383
我实在是没有耐心了 这已经连累到我丈夫了
I'm at the end of my patience when it comes to knocking my old man about.

339
00:22:22,421 --> 00:22:23,760
谁要伤害他?
Who knocked him about?

340
00:22:24,203 --> 00:22:25,875
我要是知道就好了
I wish I knew that.

341
00:22:25,912 --> 00:22:27,677
事情是今早发生的 先生
It happened this morning, sir.

342
00:22:28,324 --> 00:22:29,336
Warren先生
Mr. Warren

343
00:22:29,373 --> 00:22:35,148
是Tottenham宫廷路上 Norton & Waylight公司的计时员
he's a timekeeper at Norton & Waylight's on Tottenham Court Road.

344
00:22:35,185 --> 00:22:38,656
他必须在早晨七点钟以前出门
He has to leave the house before seven in the morning.

345
00:22:38,693 --> 00:22:41,418
要是我能和他谈谈会大有帮助
It would greatly help me if I could speak to him myself.

346
00:22:43,887 --> 00:22:45,439
好的
All right.

347
00:22:46,693 --> 00:22:48,849
小心点 福尔摩斯 他心脏不太好
Take care, Holmes, his heart.

348
00:22:48,886 --> 00:22:51,351
你来说说吧 Warren先生
Can you speak, Mr. Warren?

349
00:22:51,387 --> 00:22:55,339
我出门还没有走上10步
Well, I hadn't gone ten paces

350
00:22:56,827 --> 00:22:59,301
后面就来了两个人
before two men crept up behind me.

351
00:22:59,338 --> 00:23:01,002
拿大衣蒙住了他的头
And threw a coat over his head,

352
00:23:01,039 --> 00:23:02,654
把他塞到了马车里
bundled him into cab

353
00:23:02,691 --> 00:23:08,051
开了一段路后 在Hampstead荒地把他扔了出来
and drove off and shot him out on Hampstead Heath.

354
00:23:08,088 --> 00:23:09,730
Hampstead荒地
Hampstead Heath.

355
00:23:09,767 --> 00:23:12,914
真可怕 你看到什么了么?
Dreadful, what did you observe?

356
00:23:14,566 --> 00:23:16,292
我乘公共汽车回的家
I took a bus home.

357
00:23:16,330 --> 00:23:17,828
在这之前呢
Before the bus,

358
00:23:18,474 --> 00:23:19,570
那些人
these men,

359
00:23:20,128 --> 00:23:21,681
你有没有看清他们的长相?
did you observe their appearance?

360
00:23:21,763 --> 00:23:25,207
没有 先生 好像是变魔术一样 我被抓进去
No, sir, I was picked up as if by magic

361
00:23:25,244 --> 00:23:27,451
又被扔出来
and dropped as if by magic.

362
00:23:29,730 --> 00:23:31,981
车里至少有3个人
Three of them at least was in on it,

363
00:23:32,479 --> 00:23:33,950
也可能是4个
maybe four.

364
00:23:34,329 --> 00:23:36,049
你听见他们说话了么?
Did you hear them talk?

365
00:23:37,349 --> 00:23:41,787
其中一个用意大利语赌咒发誓
One of them swore some oaths in Italian.

366
00:23:42,116 --> 00:23:44,440
钱可不是万能的
Money is not everything.

367
00:23:44,516 --> 00:23:47,691
我今天就要把他给赶出去 就在今天
I'll have him out of here before the day is done.

368
00:23:47,995 --> 00:23:50,544
我想见见你的这个房客
I should like to meet this lodger of yours.

369
00:23:50,581 --> 00:23:52,478
他什么时候吃午饭?
What time does he take his lunch?

370
00:23:52,901 --> 00:23:54,313
一点整
One o'clock sharp.

371
00:23:54,606 --> 00:23:57,939
有没有什么地方能让我们藏起来?
Is there anywhere where we might conceal ourselves?

372
00:23:58,016 --> 00:24:00,269
有的 楼上有个储藏室
Yes, there's a box room upstairs.

373
00:24:00,695 --> 00:24:02,520
有没有一面大镜子?
Is there a looking glass?

374
00:24:02,557 --> 00:24:07,157
有的 在房间外楼梯平台那的抽屉里有一面
Yes, there's one on the chest of drawers outside on the landing.

375
00:24:07,194 --> 00:24:08,900
好极了 来吧 华生
Excellent, come, Watson.

376
00:24:09,566 --> 00:24:11,475
那我该怎么办?
What about me, then?

377
00:24:12,141 --> 00:24:13,779
我们有40分钟
We've got forty minutes.

378
00:24:32,390 --> 00:24:35,288
很明显他的敌人们弄错了
It's clear now that his enemies mistook their man.

379
00:24:35,759 --> 00:24:38,631
想都不敢想 要是他们抓到他会怎么样
What they would've done if they'd got him bears no thinking.

380
00:24:38,668 --> 00:24:39,433
可他们没有
But they didn't.

381
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:41,110
你看到了么?
Do you see what I see?

382
00:24:42,783 --> 00:24:45,286
一个带门廊和黑门的房子
A house with a porch and black door.

383
00:24:45,366 --> 00:24:46,337
有一个房间出租
With a room to let

384
00:24:46,374 --> 00:24:48,972
这样G就可以进到那里去
to which G could have access.

385
00:24:50,655 --> 00:24:53,168
福尔摩斯 我觉得我们应该通知苏格兰场
Holmes, I feel very strongly that we should inform Scotland Yard.

386
00:24:53,204 --> 00:24:54,551
还不是时候
Not yet.

387
00:24:54,588 --> 00:24:56,421
我们在监视
We are on watch,

388
00:24:57,649 --> 00:25:00,187
或许也在被监视
and may be being watched.

389
00:25:01,303 --> 00:25:03,816
让我们看看房子后面有什么吧
Let's see what lies behind these lodgings.

390
00:25:22,210 --> 00:25:23,455
他感觉怎么样?
How's he feeling?

391
00:25:23,532 --> 00:25:24,419
噢 他很好
Oh, he's all right.

392
00:25:24,456 --> 00:25:27,329
他就是喜欢小题大做
He just likes a fuss made of him.

393
00:27:15,978 --> 00:27:17,602
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes.

394
00:27:17,683 --> 00:27:18,820
锁上你的门
Bolt your door.

395
00:27:18,901 --> 00:27:20,881
在我们回来前别让任何人进来
And let no one in until we return.

396
00:27:20,954 --> 00:27:22,340
你看到他了么?
Did you see him?

397
00:27:22,414 --> 00:27:25,924
Warren太太 请相信我
Mrs. Warren, trust me.

398
00:27:32,609 --> 00:27:33,980
我不知道他什么时候回来
I don't know when he's coming back.

399
00:27:34,016 --> 00:27:35,195
他给了我一些钱
He gave me some money

400
00:27:35,232 --> 00:27:36,655
之后就再没有见过他
and I haven't seen him since.

401
00:27:36,692 --> 00:27:38,079
你说是一个外国绅士
A foreign gentlemen, you say.

402
00:27:38,117 --> 00:27:41,016
肯定是 但我不介意他是外国人
Definitely and I don't care for foreigners.

403
00:27:41,097 --> 00:27:42,412
哦 是吗
Oh really.

404
00:27:42,489 --> 00:27:44,032
要是你想租的话 先生
So if you want it gentlemen,

405
00:27:44,069 --> 00:27:47,073
我们可以签个合同
I'm sure we can come to an arrangement.

406
00:27:47,812 --> 00:27:49,756
等你看完了以后 我在大厅等你 先生
I'll be in the hall sir, when you've finished.

407
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:51,324
谢谢
Thank you.

408
00:27:53,727 --> 00:27:55,197
这什么都没有
Nothing in here.

409
00:27:56,371 --> 00:27:58,065
好极了
Perfect.

410
00:27:58,215 --> 00:27:59,491
看 华生
Look, Watson,

411
00:28:00,545 --> 00:28:02,744
公寓2楼的窗户里
the first floor window of the lodgings,

412
00:28:02,781 --> 00:28:04,929
住着我们焦虑的女士
our agitated lady.

413
00:28:06,564 --> 00:28:08,545
只需要再等几个小时
Only a few more hours to wait

414
00:28:08,617 --> 00:28:09,887
就会发信号
before the signal.

415
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:13,674
黄昏之后 G
After dusk, G.

416
00:28:15,402 --> 00:28:19,479
一切都符合为爱私奔的条件
It has all the makings of some love escapade.

417
00:28:20,272 --> 00:28:21,630
爱?
Love?

418
00:28:23,856 --> 00:28:25,984
爱或许是这件事的根源
Love may be at the root of it

419
00:28:27,266 --> 00:28:29,321
但她的脸
but her face,

420
00:28:29,562 --> 00:28:31,240
噢 华生 她的脸
oh, Watson her face

421
00:28:31,277 --> 00:28:33,337
上面写满了对生活的忧虑
She fears for her life,

422
00:28:34,294 --> 00:28:37,255
我想有一对夫妇
I consider a couple,

423
00:28:37,771 --> 00:28:39,017
来伦敦避难
seek refuge in London

424
00:28:39,054 --> 00:28:41,902
为了躲避某种威胁
from some instant and terrible fear.

425
00:28:41,982 --> 00:28:44,942
丈夫为了最大限度保证妻子的安全
The man desires her utmost safety

426
00:28:45,551 --> 00:28:47,651
而采用如此原始的方式
and arranges to communicate

427
00:28:47,722 --> 00:28:49,525
来进行联络
in such original fashion

428
00:28:49,563 --> 00:28:53,396
甚至是女房东 也不知道房客已经换人了
for not even the landlady knows of the substitution.

429
00:28:53,432 --> 00:28:57,678
字条是用印刷体写的 以防有人通过笔迹认出来
And there's printed messages to prevent the fact that she's a woman

430
00:28:57,715 --> 00:29:00,232
房客是一个女人
being revealed by her handwriting.

431
00:29:01,806 --> 00:29:03,142
看
Look.

432
00:29:04,630 --> 00:29:06,336
蜡烛和火柴
A candle and matches,

433
00:29:08,458 --> 00:29:09,627
他们的信号
Their signal.

434
00:29:10,093 --> 00:29:12,340
现在其实没这个必要
But there's no need for this now surely,

435
00:29:12,930 --> 00:29:15,171
就不能直接让他们见面么?
can't we just simply bring them together?

436
00:29:15,243 --> 00:29:17,247
你能保证我们能一直保护他们
And guarantee that we'd protect them forever

437
00:29:17,283 --> 00:29:18,930
免遭红圈会的毒手么?
from the Red Circle?

438
00:29:18,967 --> 00:29:20,230
不能
No.

439
00:29:21,574 --> 00:29:23,684
我们得让他们继续这么下去
We must let them play this thing out.

440
00:29:26,759 --> 00:29:29,046
我先回贝克街
I must return briefly to Baker Street.

441
00:29:29,472 --> 00:29:31,923
你能不能找个借口留在公寓?
Do you have reason enough to stay in the lodgings?

442
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:34,109
就说是为了Warren先生的健康
Mr. Warren's health gives me every excuse.

443
00:29:34,146 --> 00:29:37,477
或许我有必要把你的左轮手枪带来
It might be advisable for me to bring back your revolver.

444
00:29:37,785 --> 00:29:39,520
不用 我已经带着了
No need to man, I have it.

445
00:29:39,596 --> 00:29:40,882
好极了
Good, splendid.

446
00:29:48,956 --> 00:29:50,598
我们一小时后见
I'll see you within the hour.

447
00:29:56,367 --> 00:30:00,399
Hawkins 希望到头来有情人终相聚
Hawkins, journey's end with lover's meeting.

448
00:30:00,471 --> 00:30:02,724
我会主持正义的 福尔摩斯先生
I'll do you this justice, Mr. Holmes.

449
00:30:02,801 --> 00:30:03,742
我办案子的时候只要是跟您合作
I was never in a case yet

450
00:30:03,779 --> 00:30:07,016
就没有一次觉的不踏实
I didn't feel stronger for having you on my side.

451
00:30:08,123 --> 00:30:10,861
逃亡的人可能是Gennaro和Emilia Lucca
Fugitives may be Gennaro and Emilia Lucca

452
00:30:10,897 --> 00:30:12,937
如果是这样 那他们处境危险
if so in grave danger,

453
00:30:12,974 --> 00:30:15,715
很需要我们协助
expect agent imminently.

454
00:30:15,752 --> 00:30:17,959
祝好 署名Abe Rimmer
Regards, Abe Rimmer.

455
00:30:17,996 --> 00:30:19,152
他已经来了
The agent's here,

456
00:30:19,189 --> 00:30:21,028
今天早晨从纽约来的
he arrived from New York this morning.

457
00:30:21,065 --> 00:30:21,829
名字叫Leverton
His name is Leverton.

458
00:30:21,866 --> 00:30:23,997
我听说过这个名字
Leverton I know of him.

459
00:30:24,034 --> 00:30:26,925
他一直在追捕Black Gorgiano
The man he's after is Black Gorgiano,

460
00:30:27,333 --> 00:30:29,460
红圈会的头目
leader of the Red Circle.

461
00:30:30,547 --> 00:30:33,109
我们是不是这一次领先你了 福尔摩斯先生?
Do we score over you for once, Mr. Holmes?

462
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:36,522
你得更努力一点了
You must give us best some of the time.

463
00:30:38,671 --> 00:30:44,171
我想我们都应该竭尽全力
I think that we should pool our resources.

464
00:31:07,131 --> 00:31:08,381
楼上有人
There's someone up there.

465
00:31:13,638 --> 00:31:14,692
Warren太太
Mrs Warren.

466
00:31:26,823 --> 00:31:27,546
福尔摩斯
Holmes.

467
00:31:28,528 --> 00:31:30,472
让楼下保持安静
Keep the peace downstairs.

468
00:31:30,546 --> 00:31:33,215
我得和Senora Lucca说几句话
I must have a word with Senora Lucca.

469
00:31:47,664 --> 00:31:49,008
Senora Lucca
Senora Lucca,

470
00:31:49,438 --> 00:31:50,941
我是歇洛克・福尔摩斯
its Sherlock Holmes.

471
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,025
我必须和你谈谈
I must speak to you.

472
00:31:53,335 --> 00:31:54,396
哦 不
Oh no.

473
00:31:58,796 --> 00:32:01,713
你丈夫Gennaro和你都会安全的
Your husband Gennaro, will be safe, and so will you

474
00:32:01,788 --> 00:32:04,848
如果你愿意接受我们的保护
if you will place yourself in our hands.

475
00:32:10,138 --> 00:32:13,292
苏格兰场在监视这所房子
Scotland Yard is watching the house

476
00:32:13,375 --> 00:32:17,965
Leverton先生也在从纽约赶来
and Mr. Leverton is on his way from New York.

477
00:32:18,036 --> 00:32:20,538
Leverton先生?
Mr. Leverton?

478
00:32:26,665 --> 00:32:29,855
我们不会让你受到任何伤害的
We shall not let any harm come to you.

479
00:32:29,935 --> 00:32:31,702
请让我进来
Please let me in.

480
00:32:33,936 --> 00:32:35,429
好么
Please.

481
00:32:40,337 --> 00:32:42,554
我再也不上去了
I'm not going up there again.

482
00:32:42,633 --> 00:32:43,569
绝不
Never.

483
00:32:43,643 --> 00:32:44,497
亲爱的 别说傻话
Oh don't be silly dear,

484
00:32:44,533 --> 00:32:45,196
别傻了
don't be silly.

485
00:32:45,233 --> 00:32:46,889
你听到医生的话了
You know what the doctor said,

486
00:32:46,926 --> 00:32:49,235
是一只猫在抓
it was just a cat scratching.

487
00:32:49,313 --> 00:32:51,788
不 不是的 天花板都被掀起来了
No, it wasn't, it lifted.

488
00:32:51,825 --> 00:32:55,192
Hudson太太 你能给Vera倒杯茶么?
Mrs. Hudson, would you make Vera a cup of tea, please?

489
00:32:55,853 --> 00:32:57,843
这屋子里发生什么了?
What is going on in this house?

490
00:32:57,976 --> 00:33:00,619
吵吵嚷嚷 灯也不亮
Noises, lights going off,

491
00:33:01,279 --> 00:33:02,879
我快要死了
it'll be the death of me.

492
00:33:02,951 --> 00:33:03,963
噢 天呐
Oh my god.

493
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:08,769
我出生在那不勒斯附近的Posillipo
I was born in Posillipo near Naples.

494
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:11,362
我父亲是名首席律师
My father was chief lawyer.

495
00:33:12,414 --> 00:33:14,445
Gennaro没有钱 也没有地位
Gennaro had no money and no position,

496
00:33:14,482 --> 00:33:20,448
虽然没有这些 但是他英俊 有活力
nothing but his beauty, his strength and energy.

497
00:33:21,913 --> 00:33:23,586
我父亲不同意我们结婚
My father forbade the match

498
00:33:23,623 --> 00:33:25,004
我们就私奔
and we run away.

499
00:33:25,041 --> 00:33:27,342
在巴里结了婚
We were married in Bari.

500
00:33:27,931 --> 00:33:31,127
我卖掉了首饰当路费 来到了美国
I sold my jewels to bring us to America.

501
00:33:33,186 --> 00:33:35,541
一开始命运向我们微笑
Fortune smiled at first,

502
00:33:35,829 --> 00:33:37,453
Gennaro从几个暴徒手中
Gennaro saved a rich Italian

503
00:33:37,534 --> 00:33:39,843
救下了一个富有的意大利人
from some ruffians in the Bowery.

504
00:33:40,387 --> 00:33:42,529
名叫Signor Castallote
He was Signor Castallote

505
00:33:43,280 --> 00:33:47,300
经营Castallote&Zamba水果出口公司
of Castallote and Zamba the fruit importers.

506
00:33:48,285 --> 00:33:50,904
Gennaro与他情同父子
Gennaro became like a son to him.

507
00:34:02,166 --> 00:34:03,865
告诉我们这个访客的情况
Tell me about this visitor,

508
00:34:05,820 --> 00:34:08,536
这个你们从Posillipo来的朋友
this friend of your husbands from Posillipo?

509
00:34:08,811 --> 00:34:10,545
噢 他不是朋友
Oh, is no friend.

510
00:34:11,943 --> 00:34:14,208
Gennaro有一天把他带回家来
Gennaro brought him home one day.

511
00:34:14,378 --> 00:34:16,110
他们是在街上偶遇的
They had met in the street.

512
00:34:16,187 --> 00:34:17,746
以后他就经常来
He came again and again.

513
00:34:19,178 --> 00:34:22,950
他大谈什么政治和社会问题
He talked and raved about politics and social questions

514
00:34:22,988 --> 00:34:26,846
以及他的打算 还挥舞着他巨大的手臂
and what he meant to do, whirling his great arm.

515
00:34:26,882 --> 00:34:30,169
他的声音在我们的小房子里 听起来就像是打雷
His voice was like thunder in our little house.

516
00:34:30,243 --> 00:34:31,599
那你的丈夫呢?
And your husband?

517
00:34:32,762 --> 00:34:36,960
他坐在那 脸色苍白 无精打采
He sat pale and listless.

518
00:34:36,997 --> 00:34:40,093
一开始我以为他是不喜欢
At first I thought it was dislike

519
00:34:40,952 --> 00:34:43,113
后来我才明白
but then I understood

520
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:46,984
是一种深藏的恐惧
it was a deep secret fear.

521
00:34:48,402 --> 00:34:50,388
我恳求他出于对我的爱
I implored him out of love for me,

522
00:34:50,424 --> 00:34:52,239
出于我们相濡以沫的感情
by all we held dear

523
00:34:52,276 --> 00:34:55,208
告诉我为什么这个人 能给他带来这么大的阴影
to tell me why this man overshadowed him.

524
00:35:02,097 --> 00:35:04,825
在他年少不羁的时代
In his wild, young days

525
00:35:04,862 --> 00:35:08,112
全世界好像都跟他过不去
when all the world seemed against him

526
00:35:08,149 --> 00:35:10,394
他就加入了一个兄弟会
he had joined a brotherhood,

527
00:35:10,431 --> 00:35:12,295
El Chicaroso
El Chicaroso

528
00:35:12,332 --> 00:35:14,097
红圈会
the Red Circle.

529
00:35:16,043 --> 00:35:17,521
他以为它的目的仅仅是
He thought its purpose

530
00:35:17,558 --> 00:35:21,301
反对生活中的不公正
was to put right the injustice of life.

531
00:35:23,331 --> 00:35:26,155
一旦你发了那个可怕的誓
Once you've taken its dreadful oath.

532
00:35:30,050 --> 00:35:31,571
告诉我关于
Tell me about you,

533
00:35:32,414 --> 00:35:35,819
你和Gorgiano
and Gorgiano.

534
00:35:38,863 --> 00:35:43,244
我早就注意到了 当他来找我们时
I had noticed for some time when he came to us

535
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:47,307
他总是盯着我看
his eyes were always turned upon me

536
00:35:47,344 --> 00:35:51,244
那眼睛真可怕
his terrible glaring eyes.

537
00:35:51,688 --> 00:35:53,271
有一天晚上
And one evening,

538
00:35:55,238 --> 00:35:58,084
他说我唤醒了他所谓的爱
I had awakened what he called love in him.

539
00:35:58,161 --> 00:36:03,897
-Emilia 我的唯一 -那是一种野兽般的爱
-Emilia, mio solo grande. -It was the love of a brut,

540
00:36:03,933 --> 00:36:05,473
野蛮粗俗
a savage.

541
00:36:26,898 --> 00:36:28,453
几天以后
A few days later,

542
00:36:28,490 --> 00:36:30,737
红圈会有一个会议
there was a Red Circle meeting.

543
00:36:33,508 --> 00:36:36,248
他们勒索Signor Castallote
Signor Castallote had been approached for money

544
00:36:36,326 --> 00:36:37,686
却遭到了拒绝
and had refused them.

545
00:36:38,563 --> 00:36:40,814
于是他们计划杀了他
Now they planned to kill him,

546
00:36:41,441 --> 00:36:43,201
通过抽签来决定谁动手
they drew lots.

547
00:36:50,730 --> 00:36:52,942
<i>这是早就安排好的</i>
<i>It was fixed.</i>

548
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:56,640
<i>因为我拒绝了Gorgiano 他要报复</i>
<i>It was Gorgiano's revenge for my rejecting him.</i>

549
00:37:04,682 --> 00:37:06,577
我在这世上
My dearest friend,

550
00:37:10,143 --> 00:37:12,242
最好的朋友
in all the world.

551
00:37:13,065 --> 00:37:15,118
然后你们一起去了警察局?
And then you both went to the police?

552
00:37:15,693 --> 00:37:17,386
我一个人去的
I went alone.

553
00:37:18,076 --> 00:37:19,047
真勇敢
That was brave.

554
00:37:19,120 --> 00:37:21,299
就算是 可这有什么用呢?
Yes, but what has it done?

555
00:37:21,973 --> 00:37:24,960
我们被迫逃走 我们的朋友还是难逃一死
They got us away but friends still die.

556
00:37:24,997 --> 00:37:27,538
我们永远逃不出那野兽的控制 永远
We shall never be rid of that beast, never

557
00:37:29,399 --> 00:37:30,937
现在你得走了
and now you must go.

558
00:37:31,436 --> 00:37:32,130
我已经说的太多了
I've said too much,

559
00:37:32,167 --> 00:37:34,281
已经违背了对我丈夫的许诺
I've broken my promise to my husband,

560
00:37:34,861 --> 00:37:37,632
快走吧 求你了
go please, go.

561
00:38:33,016 --> 00:38:34,975
Enrico会感到欣慰的
Enrico would have wished it.

562
00:38:35,012 --> 00:38:37,094
开始新的生活吧
Go sail to a new life.

563
00:38:38,131 --> 00:38:39,305
Gracias
Gracias.

564
00:39:17,723 --> 00:39:20,644
他不能整夜待在这里
He can't stay here all night.

565
00:39:23,151 --> 00:39:26,449
要是有必要 他会的 是么 医生?
Well if he has to won't you, Doctor?

566
00:39:29,054 --> 00:39:33,699
好吧 那样的话 我们来玩会惠斯特纸牌吧
Well, in that case I wouldn't mind a game of whist.

567
00:39:34,809 --> 00:39:37,506
你玩惠斯特纸牌么 医生?
Do you play whist, Doctor?

568
00:40:00,899 --> 00:40:02,815
福尔摩斯先生?
Mr. Holmes?

569
00:40:03,927 --> 00:40:05,982
Emilia
Emilia.

570
00:40:07,265 --> 00:40:12,736
Emilia 我的爱
Emilia, mi amore.

571
00:40:31,341 --> 00:40:32,782
Hawkins
Hawkins.

572
00:40:34,020 --> 00:40:36,482
我已经安排了人监视 福尔摩斯先生
I've set my men on watch, Mr. Holmes.

573
00:40:37,290 --> 00:40:38,850
你在期待什么?
What are you expecting to happen?

574
00:40:39,274 --> 00:40:42,820
不止一次 侦查行动的作用有限
Well, there are times when the art of detection is of little use.

575
00:40:44,841 --> 00:40:47,658
得等待那些无法预知的事发生
We must wait upon the unpredictable.

576
00:40:48,146 --> 00:40:50,558
我也有这样的经验
I've had some experience of that in my time.

577
00:40:51,173 --> 00:40:55,974
我可以说 我们要等的是Signora Lucca的丈夫
I can say only that we are expecting Signora Lucca's husband.

578
00:40:57,191 --> 00:40:58,578
你得放他过去
You must let him pass.

579
00:40:58,652 --> 00:41:00,276
你的人不要干扰他
Your men must not distract him.

580
00:41:00,357 --> 00:41:01,794
-他们知道的 -很好
They know that. Fine.

581
00:41:02,167 --> 00:41:04,233
-那我们要抓的凶手呢? -噢 他就在附近
-And our murderer? -Oh, he is about.

582
00:41:06,001 --> 00:41:07,621
某个地方
Somewhere,

583
00:41:10,098 --> 00:41:11,474
等待机会下手
waiting his chance.

584
00:41:11,511 --> 00:41:14,293
美国的Leverton给了我一份详尽的描述
I have a good description from the American Leverton,

585
00:41:14,448 --> 00:41:15,760
我们都准备好了
we'll be ready.

586
00:41:18,483 --> 00:41:19,550
看
Look.

587
00:41:22,590 --> 00:41:23,596
华生
Watson.

588
00:42:05,835 --> 00:42:07,246
Signora Lucca
Signora Lucca,

589
00:42:07,713 --> 00:42:09,136
你必须告诉我暗号
you must give me the signal.

590
00:42:09,209 --> 00:42:10,836
走开 我再不会相信你了
Go away, I don't trust you.

591
00:42:10,948 --> 00:42:12,964
除了我丈夫 我谁也不信
I trust no one but my husband.

592
00:42:13,036 --> 00:42:14,210
非常感谢你 医生
I'm obliged to you, Doctor.

593
00:42:14,289 --> 00:42:17,135
最好不要动弹
The main thing is just to keep this still as possible.

594
00:42:17,211 --> 00:42:17,901
好的
Fine.

595
00:42:19,160 --> 00:42:21,239
-福尔摩斯先生 -福尔摩斯
-Mr. Holmes. -Holmes.

596
00:42:21,276 --> 00:42:23,985
这是平克顿侦探事务所的 Leverton先生
This is Mr. Leverton of the Pinkerton Agency.

597
00:42:24,066 --> 00:42:28,656
破获长岛山洞奇案的Leverton么
Leverton, of the Long Island Cave mystery

598
00:42:28,727 --> 00:42:30,671
很荣幸见到你
I'm honored to meet you.

599
00:42:30,745 --> 00:42:31,919
是我的荣幸 先生
The honor is mine, sir.

600
00:42:31,997 --> 00:42:34,013
好吧
Well, well, well.

601
00:42:34,085 --> 00:42:35,536
很可惜这幅模样见你
I'm sorry we had to meet like this.

602
00:42:35,617 --> 00:42:36,560
你很勇敢
You're a brave man,

603
00:42:36,597 --> 00:42:38,372
我看到你在屋顶
I saw you on the roof.

604
00:42:39,339 --> 00:42:41,770
当你毕生时间都用来追踪这件事的时候
When you're on the trail of a lifetime, Mr. Holmes,

605
00:42:41,844 --> 00:42:43,920
你也会把个人安全
you put all thoughts of personal safety

606
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:46,052
置之度外的 福尔摩斯先生
out of your mind.

607
00:42:46,122 --> 00:42:47,924
我想那混蛋跑掉了
The brute got away I suppose?

608
00:42:48,001 --> 00:42:50,432
是的 但他会回来的
Yes, but he'll be back soon.

609
00:42:50,506 --> 00:42:52,973
这房子里有
There's something in this house

610
00:42:53,046 --> 00:42:54,778
他梦寐以求的
that he wants badly.

611
00:42:54,855 --> 00:42:55,498
噢 是的 我知道
Oh, yes, I know.

612
00:42:55,535 --> 00:42:57,202
谢谢你 医生 我很好 真的很好
Thank you, Doctor, I'm fine, just fine.

613
00:42:57,239 --> 00:42:59,379
楼上的女士安全么?
Is the lady upstairs, safe?

614
00:42:59,416 --> 00:43:01,555
是的 但不再相信任何人
Yes, but trusting no one.

615
00:43:01,779 --> 00:43:03,155
所以我们必须等待
And so we must wait

616
00:43:03,192 --> 00:43:05,198
他丈夫发出的暗号
for her husband's signal.

617
00:43:05,605 --> 00:43:06,858
什么暗号 福尔摩斯先生?
What signal, Mr. Holmes?

618
00:43:17,749 --> 00:43:19,420
Leverton 灯
Leverton, the lamp.

619
00:43:22,271 --> 00:43:25,356
这么说Gennaro Lucca就在那儿?
So Gennaro Lucca is over there now?

620
00:43:25,436 --> 00:43:27,261
还没有 但我想他会来的
Not yet but he will be I hope.

621
00:43:27,298 --> 00:43:30,030
当我到伦敦的时候 我也找不到Lucca
I couldn't find Lucca when I got to London.

622
00:43:30,067 --> 00:43:32,650
我们通过Enrico Firmani进行联系
My contact was Enrico Firmani

623
00:43:32,687 --> 00:43:34,567
但那家伙找到了他
but the brute reached him first

624
00:43:34,604 --> 00:43:37,936
在杀死他之前肯定也让他开口了
and he must have made him talk before killing him.

625
00:43:37,973 --> 00:43:40,459
我们是不是该上楼去看看Lucca夫人?
Shall we not go upstairs to reassure Mrs. Lucca?

626
00:43:40,537 --> 00:43:41,947
她不会让我们进到房间里去的 华生
She won't admit us, Watson.

627
00:43:42,998 --> 00:43:44,595
她现在只听她丈夫的
She'll only answer to her husband.

628
00:43:44,676 --> 00:43:47,404
噢 看哪 是Hawkins
Oh, look, Hawkins

629
00:43:48,190 --> 00:43:49,964
不是很显眼
not too conspicuous.

630
00:43:50,313 --> 00:43:53,754
对 Hawkins警督 他看来来很能干
Yes, Inspector Hawkins, he seems an able fellow.

631
00:43:53,791 --> 00:43:55,960
是苏格兰场最好的一个
One of Scotland Yard's finest.

632
00:43:55,997 --> 00:43:57,844
业务熟练
He knows his business.

633
00:44:15,710 --> 00:44:16,971
先生们
Gentlemen,

634
00:44:18,146 --> 00:44:21,751
Gennaro Lucca刚刚进来
Gennaro Lucca has just gone in.

635
00:44:22,808 --> 00:44:24,270
目前为止一切顺利
So far so good.

636
00:44:24,966 --> 00:44:26,388
夫人是在红圈会计划要杀掉Castallote
Mrs. Lucca came to us

637
00:44:26,461 --> 00:44:29,140
那天晚上来找我们的
the night the Red Circle planned to kill Castallote.

638
00:44:30,636 --> 00:44:33,193
他们已经杀掉了他的合伙人Zamba
They'd already murdered his partner Zamba.

639
00:44:34,393 --> 00:44:36,236
我们设法把团伙成员一网打尽
We managed to round up most of the gang

640
00:44:36,273 --> 00:44:40,089
但那个Black Gorgiano漏网了
but Black Gorgiano slipped the net.

641
00:44:41,665 --> 00:44:43,264
一听说他来英国
When we heard he'd left for England,

642
00:44:43,301 --> 00:44:45,921
我也就尽快赶来了
I followed after him fast as I could.

643
00:44:47,490 --> 00:44:48,628
我和苏格兰场取得了联系
I got in touch with Scotland Yard

644
00:44:48,665 --> 00:44:51,322
他却没有踪影了
but he'd gone to ground.

645
00:45:52,743 --> 00:45:54,546
开始发出暗号了 是什么意思?
There's a single light, what does it mean?

646
00:45:55,553 --> 00:45:56,812
两个灯光
Two lights.

647
00:46:00,745 --> 00:46:03,712
-消失了 -不 又有了
-Gone. -No, no, there it is again.

648
00:46:06,903 --> 00:46:10,893
缓慢的闪三下
Three lights measured slow.

649
00:46:12,122 --> 00:46:14,468
他要说什么 到底什么意思?
What's he saying, what does it mean?

650
00:46:14,871 --> 00:46:15,736
没什么意思
Nothing,

651
00:46:15,810 --> 00:46:16,620
没什么
nothing.

652
00:46:18,281 --> 00:46:21,453
但他下一步肯定是要确认一下
But his next actions must confirm it.

653
00:46:21,968 --> 00:46:26,015
他肯定是来这里等她
He must come here to collect her.

654
00:46:33,136 --> 00:46:34,474
又消失了
It's gone.

655
00:46:35,120 --> 00:46:36,543
收到消息了
The message received.

656
00:46:36,615 --> 00:46:37,649
什么消息?
But what message?

657
00:46:43,469 --> 00:46:45,241
Gennaro
Gennaro.

658
00:46:46,948 --> 00:46:50,804
我最好的朋友
My dearest friend in all the world,

659
00:46:52,515 --> 00:46:56,974
和兄弟会的叛徒
and betrayer of the brotherhood.

660
00:46:59,542 --> 00:47:01,739
这不是在发信号 有个人跟他在一起
There's no message there's somebody with him.

661
00:47:04,030 --> 00:47:05,024
华生?
Watson?

662
00:47:06,118 --> 00:47:07,470
你听到了么 福尔摩斯?
Did you hear that, Holmes?

663
00:47:07,544 --> 00:47:09,168
是的 危险
Yeah, danger.

664
00:47:09,249 --> 00:47:12,024
天哪 看 她跑出来了 跑到街上了
My God, look she's out there on the street.

665
00:47:12,102 --> 00:47:13,347
华生
Watson.

666
00:47:32,838 --> 00:47:35,962
Hawkins 你要抓的人在那
Hawkins Your murderer is up there.

667
00:47:36,039 --> 00:47:38,091
不可能 这只有一个入口
Impossible, there's only one entrance.

668
00:47:38,161 --> 00:47:39,655
等一下 他是我的人 Hawkins
Just a minute he's mine, Hawkins,

669
00:47:39,726 --> 00:47:41,184
-我来负责 -不 你不能 先生
-I'll take responsibility. -No you won't sir,

670
00:47:41,221 --> 00:47:43,802
伦敦的事由伦敦警方负责
London dangers are up to the London force.

671
00:47:46,058 --> 00:47:47,444
Gennaro
Gennaro.

672
00:48:07,942 --> 00:48:09,495
Emilia
Emilia.

673
00:48:21,198 --> 00:48:23,704
华生 带他们离开这个恐怖的地方
Watson, take them away from this horror.

674
00:48:52,197 --> 00:48:54,217
请把船票给我 先生
I'll take those tickets, sir.

675
00:48:55,816 --> 00:48:59,329
求求你 我们的船黎明时起锚
Please, our ship sales at dawn.

676
00:49:07,505 --> 00:49:09,314
你打算把它怎么办 警督?
What are you going to do with him, Inspector?

677
00:49:09,627 --> 00:49:12,377
他将被逮捕 并以谋杀Gorgiano的罪名被指控
He'll be arrested and tried for the murder of Gorgiano,

678
00:49:12,415 --> 00:49:14,088
法律就是法律
that is the law.

679
00:49:14,742 --> 00:49:17,497
我不知道你们英国的法律会怎么对他
Well, I don't know what your British law may be

680
00:49:17,535 --> 00:49:19,110
但我想要是在纽约
but I guess that in New York,

681
00:49:19,147 --> 00:49:22,888
这位女士的丈夫会收到很多的感谢信
this lady's husband will receive a pretty general vote of thanks.

682
00:49:25,249 --> 00:49:27,996
这世上没有哪一个法官 会给这个男人判刑
There's not a judge on earth that will condemn this man.

683
00:49:28,504 --> 00:49:31,444
我想Lucca夫妇没有什么好担心的
I don't think Mr. And Mrs. Lucca have too much to fear

684
00:49:31,824 --> 00:49:33,670
但我们还是得遵守法律程序
but we have to go through the procedures.

685
00:49:34,573 --> 00:49:35,994
带他们下楼
Take them downstairs.

686
00:49:42,191 --> 00:49:44,994
要是你一个人在这里 福尔摩斯先生
No doubt if you'd been here on your own, Mr. Holmes,

687
00:49:45,149 --> 00:49:47,239
你会有不同的解决方法吧
you'd have found a different solution.

688
00:49:47,515 --> 00:49:50,175
我们生活在法律之下 警督
The law is what we live with, Inspector.

689
00:49:51,097 --> 00:49:56,719
但有的时候正义更难实现
Justice is sometimes harder to achieve.

690
00:49:57,466 --> 00:49:59,665
我还是不明白 你是怎么一开始
What I still don't understand is how you came to be mixed up

691
00:49:59,701 --> 00:50:00,934
就卷到这件事里来的
in all this in the first place.

692
00:50:00,971 --> 00:50:02,960
晚安警督
Good night, Inspector.

693
00:50:04,229 --> 00:50:05,929
晚安 福尔摩斯先生
Good night, Mr. Holmes.

694
00:50:37,545 --> 00:50:40,599
<i>看来英国的司法 对这对年轻夫妇很友善</i>
<i>English justice looked kindly on the young couple</i>

695
00:50:40,636 --> 00:50:43,345
<i>不久 他们就去了澳大利亚</i>
<i>and soon afterwards they left for Australia.</i>

696
00:50:44,423 --> 00:50:46,824
<i>在那里终于摆脱了红圈会的威胁</i>
<i>There they found a new and happier life</i>

697
00:50:46,904 --> 00:50:50,242
<i>过着新的幸福生活</i>
<i>free from the threat of the Red Circle.</i>

698
00:50:54,670 --> 00:50:59,779

